[b]Conquerors![/b]

It’s me, your friendly community manager, Katten, bringing you exciting news! We're kicking off our [b]free-to-play event[/b], launching our [b]new base game[/b], and starting our [b]grandest sale yet![/b] So let’s dive into the details below!

[h2]Free-to-Play![/h2]
The [b]Europa Universalis IV[/b] base game is now [b]free to play[/b] for everyone until [b]October 23rd at 19:00 CEST![/b] Whether you have a friend or a family member you want to invite into a multiplayer game or challenge for an achievement hunt, send them to the base game store page below to start playing right now!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/236850/Europa_Universalis_IV/

[h2]The New Base Game[/h2]
We’ve just released our brand-new base game! This version includes the former DLCs [b]“Rights of Man,” “Art of War,” “Common Sense,”[/b] and the [b]“Digital Extreme Upgrade.”[/b] If you didn't own these DLCs previously, you now have access to them, providing a better experience for new players!

[h2]The Grandest Sale[/h2]
We haven't forgotten about our veteran players! Our grandest sale is now live, featuring an updated [b]Ultimate Edition[/b] that includes [b]all expansions and immersion packs![/b] Enjoy a massive [b]75% base discount[/b], with an additional sale discount that brings it to [b]87%![/b] If you’re missing any DLCs, this is the best deal ever—check it out below!

https://store.steampowered.com/bundle/22085/Europa_Universalis_IV_Ultimate_Bundle/

If you prefer not to buy the dynamic bundle, you can also purchase all the DLCs individually below:

